OL,3,CWhy your holiday could cost an extra
OL,4,C#200 this summer
OL,6,FPackage holidays to popular European
OL,7,Fdestinations are up to 11.5% more
OL,8,Fexpensive this year compared with
OL,9,F2024, according to new analysis.
OL,11,FConsumer group Which? said this is
OL,12,Fbecause of a range of factors,
OL,13,Fincluding high demand, rising energy
OL,14,Fcosts for hotels, and capacity
OL,15,Fconstraints for airlines.
OL,17,FThe Black Sea coast of Bulgaria is one
OL,18,Fof the destinations that have seen the
OL,19,Fmost significant increase.
