OL,3,CWhy your holiday could cost an extra
OL,4,C#200 this summer
OL,6,FThe average per person price for a
OL,7,Fseven-day break in that location has
OL,8,Frisen by 11.5% from #1,038 to #1,157.
OL,10,FThat means a couple will have to find
OL,11,Fan extra #238 on average to make a
OL,12,Fbooking.
OL,14,FOther destinations with high average
OL,15,Fprice rises were found to be Italy (up
OL,16,F7.4%), Portugal (up 6.8%) and Cyprus
OL,17,F(up 6.4%).
OL,19,FAcross all locations, the average
OL,20,Fincrease was 4.2%.
