OL,3,CWhy your holiday could cost an extra
OL,4,C#200 this summer
OL,6,FWhich? said this is compared with the
OL,7,FUK's Consumer Prices Index measure of
OL,8,Finflation of 2.5% in the year to
OL,9,FDecember 2024, whereas the rate of
OL,10,Finflation in the euro area was 2.4%.
OL,12,FHowever, package holiday prices have
OL,13,Ffallen in a handful of summer holiday
OL,14,Fhotspots, such as Ibiza (down 6.4%)
OL,15,Fand Tenerife (down 2.0%).
