OL,3,CWhy your holiday could cost an extra
OL,4,C#200 this summer
OL,6,FRory Boland, editor of magazine Which?
OL,7,FTravel, said: "Booking early is almost
OL,8,Falways your best chance of securing
OL,9,Fthe best rate ` so now is the best
OL,10,Ftime to get the cheapest prices on
OL,11,Fsummer holidays.
OL,13,F"Take the time to shop around, and if
OL,14,Fyou're holidaying with kids, consider
OL,15,Ftravelling in the last week of the
OL,16,Fsummer holidays, as we've previously
OL,17,Ffound this can be the cheapest week in
OL,18,Fthe peak season."
